messages.messageBody:
At our local HS/school store, they have these posters that are blck and white
printed with questions about a topic (I think they have All about Me, States,
similar titles) places to draw pictures, timelines, It's really pretty
interesting!
Check and see if there is something like that that she would enjoy.
*~*Elissa Jill*~*
unschooling Momma to 3 beautiful brilliant people
Loving partner for life to Joey
terrible guitarist, fair singer and happy woman.
